{"tid":2312173,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月內兩高官買樓代表乜？","createTime":"2020-12-04T15:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T16:43:14.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce583a6177844474ec434a1b512f86e7eba06b6","tid":2312173,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"一個月內兩發展局高官買樓  <br />\n<br />\n今次副秘書長<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\">麥成章</span></span><br />\n2650萬購西半山豪宅<br />\n<br />\n疫情未有阻礙高官們的入市步伐，近日再有政府官員購入物業，為過去一個月第二宗。據土地註冊處資料，西半山帝豪閣C座低層2室，面積1,196平方呎，以2,650萬元成交，呎價約22,157元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2820122/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2820122%2F2_1024.jpg&h=d6522ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料顯示，上址由<span class=\"blue\">麥成章（</span>MAK SHING CHEUNG）及何美貞（HO MEI CHING FIONA）聯名買入，麥氏與發展局副秘書長同名，疑似為同一人。<br />\n<br />\n顏色一目瞭然啦"},{"pid":"75a166e516d92293419d2888d2ba9fe077618c88","tid":2312173,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:00:51.000Z","msg":"事實上，過去一個月有兩宗官員入市的個案，而且兩宗成交的新買家均為發展局相關官員。對上一宗買賣的物業，由發展局副局長廖振新（LIU CHUN SAN）於10月底購入，單位位於馬鞍山銀湖‧天峰6座低層B室，以2,335萬元成交"},{"pid":"17fc0a563d4898cfe0f344842b28c8900d8d2357","tid":2312173,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"高官唔計"},{"pid":"ee0581cc8db02618532ae180d14f7495db25ff46","tid":2312173,"uid":145769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"你最近生意點？ 有無成交？"},{"pid":"aad2cdc4987904db6d6f7c3ae367800e11a197f7","tid":2312173,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ee0581cc8db02618532ae180d14f7495db25ff46","tid":2312173,"uid":145769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"你最近生意點？ 有無成交？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"冇生意